Cary.White Oak Township, Wake County, North C:
White Oak Township (also designated Township 20) is one of twenty townships within Wake County, North Carolina, in the United States. As of the 2010 census, White Oak Township had a population of 72,894, an 88.3% increase over 2000.
White Oak Township, occupying 52.9 square miles (137.1 km2) in western Wake County, includes the bulk of the town of Apex and portions of the town of Cary.
